    "body": "Before this commit, a subfolder with the same name as the root/source folder would be ignored from the coverage reports (see https://github.com/mozilla/grcov/issues/483). This was occurring because the ancestor of the subfolder was being pruned (because it matched the end of the source folder) in the method used to guess the absolute path. This resulted in an incorrect guess of the absolute path.\r\n\r\nWith this commit, we first check whether the join of the subfolder relative path with the source folder exists, and if so, return it as the guess of the absolute path. If the join doesn't exist, we use the previous guess method.",
